# Backend - WiFi Management API Server
# NestJS 11 + Prisma 7 + PostgreSQL 18 + Redis 8 + BullMQ 5

Direktori ini berisi source code untuk REST API backend.

## Stack
- NestJS 11 (TypeScript 6.x)
- Prisma ORM 7.x + PostgreSQL 18
- Redis 8 + BullMQ 5.x (Queue Worker)
- JWT Authentication (jsonwebtoken 9.x)
- PDFKit 0.18.x (Generate PDF voucher)
- @nestjs/swagger 8.x (Auto-generated API Docs)

## Jalankan Development
```bash
pnpm install
cp .env.example .env
pnpm prisma migrate dev
pnpm run start:dev
```

| Service | URL |
|---|---|
| API Server | http://localhost:4000 |
| Swagger API Docs | http://localhost:4000/api/docs |
| Bull Board (Queue) | http://localhost:4000/bull-board |

## Struktur Module
```
src/modules/
├── auth/           → Login, JWT guard, strategy
├── servers/        → CRUD MikroTik servers
├── mikrotik/       → MikroTik API client (shared service)
├── profiles/       → Hotspot user profile
├── vouchers/       → Generate single & batch voucher
├── pos/            → POS integration endpoint
├── monitoring/     → Active users real-time
├── ai/             → AI analysis (skeleton, siap pakai API)
└── logs/           → Activity log
```
